name: valleydesignbuild
description: ### Getting Started 1. Install Node.js using [NVM](http://github.com/creationix/nvm) for OSX/Linux or by going to [Nodejs.org](http://nodejs.org) for Windows 2. ```npm install -g zab``` 3. ```zab watch --open``` 4. ```zab --help``` for more info 5. Visit us at [zab.io](http://zab.io)
